org.upmc.electisim

Class StateBuffer

  • Object
    • CircularBuffer<SimulationState>
      • StateBuffer

  • public class StateBuffer
extends CircularBuffer<SimulationState>
    The buffer containing all the states of the simulation. All the stepping operations are performed on this data structure. Is essentially similar to a circular buffer with few stepping operations on top. NOTE : It should be noted that this class is very powerful and holds much power on the simulation process, hence why it should be only seldomly exposed to the user, if ever.
